author: xusd320
message:
feat(turbo-tasks-hash): update twox-hash (#82518)

### What
Avoid using two versions of `twox-hash`

files.patch:
@@ -9411,7 +9411,7 @@ name = "turbo-tasks-hash"
 version = "0.1.0"
 dependencies = [
  "turbo-tasks-macros",
- "twox-hash 1.6.3",
+ "twox-hash 2.1.0",
 ]
 
 [[package]]
@@ -10113,7 +10113,6 @@ source = "registry+https://github.com/rust-lang/crates.io-index"
 checksum = "97fee6b57c6a41524a810daee9286c02d7752c4253064d0b05472833a438f675"
 dependencies = [
  "cfg-if",
- "rand 0.8.5",
  "static_assertions",
 ]

@@ -22,7 +22,10 @@ exclude = ["crates/next-error-code-swc-plugin"]
 too_many_arguments = "allow"
 
 [workspace.lints.rust]
-unexpected_cfgs = { level = "warn", check-cfg = ['cfg(rust_analyzer)', 'cfg(fuzzing)'] }
+unexpected_cfgs = { level = "warn", check-cfg = [
+  'cfg(rust_analyzer)',
+  'cfg(fuzzing)',
+] }
 
 # This crate is particularly sensitive to compiler optimizations
 [profile.dev.package.turbo-persistence]
@@ -370,22 +373,22 @@ lightningcss = { version = "1.0.0-alpha.67", features = [
   "serde",
   "visitor",
   "into_owned",
-  "browserslist"
+  "browserslist",
 ] }

   "visitor",
 ] }

-    "napi3",
-    "serde-json",
-    "tokio_rt",
-    "error_anyhow",
-    # Lightningcss uses this features
-    "napi4",
-    "napi5",
-    "compat-mode"
+  "napi3",
+  "serde-json",
+  "tokio_rt",

+  "napi4",
+  "napi5",
+  "compat-mode",
 ] }

+vergen = { version = "9.0.6", features = ["cargo"] }
